by using the array to topdown initialize the middle result to avoid duplicated 
computing. but the time is 2 minites and 36 seconds when parameter is 44;

the using of array makes the program slower.
So ,we need to change the recursion into the loop.

//*****************************************************************************
Finially, the result of the optimalize time is 0.01 seconds.
which is obveriously faster than the implementation of recursion iterator.

